Sentencas: A computer model is developed, capable of predicting the flow distribution along the height of a fuel-cell stack.
Titulo: Computational analysis of the gas-flow distribution in solid oxide fuel cell stacks

Sentencas: The model distinguishes a number of hydraulic resistances that are linked in series and parallel, thus forming a network to simulate the gas flow and pressure distribution in a stack.
Titulo: Computational analysis of the gas-flow distribution in solid oxide fuel cell stacks

Sentencas: The hydraulic resistances are found from analytical solutions or from tabulated data inferred from measurements.
Titulo: Computational analysis of the gas-flow distribution in solid oxide fuel cell stacks

Sentencas: The electrochemistry of the stack is simulated by adding or subtracting gas in the active cell area.
Titulo: Computational analysis of the gas-flow distribution in solid oxide fuel cell stacks

Sentencas: The model is tested on an assumed separator-plate geometry and stacking height.
Titulo: Computational analysis of the gas-flow distribution in solid oxide fuel cell stacks
